{"tid":1028034,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"對於將來有啲迷惘","createTime":"2019-02-19T08:15:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T02:42:27.000Z","uid":201552,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b4ae33450fa0c69f163becb6f739fe14d59ac784","tid":1028034,"uid":201552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:15:52.000Z","msg":"喺space讀緊hd，但讀落有啲悶，day off啲日子完全唔想掂啲notes，轉course我又驚自己又唔鍾意。簡單啲講，就係對自己冇自信，對自己鍾意嘅嘢都係冇自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以上年揀咗hd讀，諗住衰極都叫hd畢業。但而家愈讀愈悶，唔知想點。<br />\n<br />\n諗落其實自己qui咗，做兼職，然後再進修都得，workload少啲，學費又平啲，自己又負擔到，唔洗痴屋企，仲可以搬出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家一個星期返3日學，2日part time，老母仲好似想我比返家用咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：公屋撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dbdd2df7d9cd0ee431348a9724b7b2cced8d8f3","tid":1028034,"uid":39496,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:30:51.000Z","msg":"人生已完"},{"pid":"33dcb55246ba441eb77685d66194ed28c608dbfd","tid":1028034,"uid":201552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dbdd2df7d9cd0ee431348a9724b7b2cced8d8f3","tid":1028034,"uid":39496,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:30:51.000Z","msg":"人生已完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T09:31:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪得返搬出去住呢條路，有時唔想咁極端，但事實好似就係得咁"},{"pid":"af42634b1452f70a4aa5000a6e56298711fb6250","tid":1028034,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T09:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404b0bfa04983de9b36c5015b464f8cf854fbab5","tid":1028034,"uid":175598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-1